## Event [/v1/event/{event_slug}]
A Event is the other central object utilized by the PurAí API. It has
rich text and annotations which comprise all of the content a users sees in
their feed. Posts are closely tied to the follow graph.

+ Parameters
    + event_slug: `sample-event` (string) - The slug of the Event.

